high_descs: Turn right and begin walking across the room, then hang a right and walk up to the sink.
Pick up the tomato off of the counter to the left of the sink.
Turn right and walk forward, then hang a right and walk up to the fridge.
Open the fridge and put the tomato inside then close the door, after a couple seconds open the fridge back up and remove the now chilled tomato then close the door.
Turn right and walk forward, then turn left to face the counter.
Put the chilled tomato on the front edge of the counter.
anns.task_desc: Put a chilled tomato on the counter.

high_descs: turn right and walk over to the sink on the right up ahead
grab a tomato off of the left side of the sink
turn around and walk over to the fridge at the end of the room on the left
place the tomato inside the fridge, let it cool, then take it back out
move to the right a bit and face the kitchen counter to the left of the stove
place the tomato down on top of the kitchen counter there
anns.task_desc: place a cooled tomato down on top of the kitchen counter

high_descs: Turn to your right and go to the left side of the sink beside the coffee maker.
Pick up the Tomato off the counter top.
Turn to your right and go back to the refrigerator.
Open the bottom door of the refrigerator and place on the middle shelf now close the refrigerator.
Let the Tomato cool and then remove it from the refrigerator.
After you have you closed refrigerator door place the tomato on the counter top to the right of you.
anns.task_desc: Chill a tomato in the refrigerator and place it on the counter.
